<h2>Information to Include</h2>

<ul>
<li>Your TikTok username (if applicable)</li>
<li>The email address associated with your request</li>
<li>A statement requesting account and data deletion</li>
</ul>

<h2>What Happens Next</h2>

<p>
After receiving your request, we will review and process the deletion request within a reasonable period of time.
</p>

<p>
Account-related information stored by Luca Hayes Content Platform will be removed where applicable, except where retention is required for legal, security or operational purposes.
</p>

